{"tid":1097882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國將伊朗革命衞隊列為「外國恐怖組織」","createTime":"2019-04-08T16:05:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T17:19:59.000Z","uid":28765,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ca9038cfd93a9dccd8d79d5dd8e22d88191e94ee","tid":1097882,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T16:05:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190408/large/1554734310_21e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190408%2Flarge%2F1554734310_21e1.jpg&h=62980d75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國總統特朗普周一宣佈，將伊朗革命衞隊定性為「外國恐怖組織」，是華府首次將外國軍隊列為恐怖組織。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在聲明中形容，今次行動「確認了一個事實，伊朗不只是恐怖主義的支持者，伊朗革命衞隊更積極參與、資助和推動恐怖主義成為治國的工具」。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧表示，行動會在一周內生效，亦向全球銀行及企業作出警告，「全球企業及銀行現時有一個明確的責任，就是確保公司的金融交易不涉及伊朗革命衞隊」。<br />\n<br />\n分析指，特朗普的破天荒之舉可能會開了先例，美國軍方及情報人員日後會對其他不友好政府採取類似行動。美國過去已將革命衞隊隊員或有關連人士列入黑名單，但從未針對整個組織。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190408/59465423\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190408%2F59465423&d=vUt%2FZqt5lAJzOS14TgBfp8ls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=d83316ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190408%2F59465423&h=86feb4d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190408/59465423</a>"},{"pid":"6189aef31f787acc5c11a03778f7cdd936b39979","tid":1097882,"uid":155095,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T16:08:36.000Z","msg":"How about this ?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DGJWVKgVYAAEjWB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDGJWVKgVYAAEjWB.jpg&h=f9fe5a95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2096e3c452e2c72a7724c31c464a346f8e952ebd","tid":1097882,"uid":34949,"l